{"version":"https://jsonfeed.org/version/1","title":"home ✧ errbufferoverfl","description":"Recent content in home on errbufferoverfl","home_page_url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/","feed_url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/index.json","items":[{"title":"Tools","date_published":"2023-08-09T22:10:22+10:00","date_modified":"2023-08-09T22:11:51+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/tools/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/tools/","content_html":""},{"title":"Bookmarks","date_published":"2023-08-09T22:08:42+10:00","date_modified":"2023-08-09T22:09:58+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/bookmarks/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/bookmarks/","content_html":""},{"title":"Notes","date_published":"2023-08-09T12:22:00+10:00","date_modified":"2023-08-12T08:09:44+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/notes/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/notes/","content_html":""},{"title":"bookmarks","date_published":"2023-08-06T10:00:22+10:00","date_modified":"2023-08-06T22:24:20+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/bookmarks/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/bookmarks/","content_html":"\u003cp\u003e%% Begin Waypoint %%\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/bookmarks/archive-stories/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/bookmarks/archive-stories/\"\u003earchive-stories\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/bookmarks/flask-documentation/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/bookmarks/flask-documentation/\"\u003eflask-documentation\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/bookmarks/gold-mafia-episode-1-the-laundry-service/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/bookmarks/gold-mafia-episode-1-the-laundry-service/\"\u003egold-mafia-episode-1-the-laundry-service\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/bookmarks/oauth-20-dynamic-client-registration-protocol/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/bookmarks/oauth-20-dynamic-client-registration-protocol/\"\u003eoauth-20-dynamic-client-registration-protocol\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/bookmarks/police-are-not-primarily-crime-fighters-according-to-the-data/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/bookmarks/police-are-not-primarily-crime-fighters-according-to-the-data/\"\u003epolice-are-not-primarily-crime-fighters-according-to-the-data\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/bookmarks/python-patterns/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/bookmarks/python-patterns/\"\u003epython-patterns\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/bookmarks/refactoring-guru/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/bookmarks/refactoring-guru/\"\u003erefactoring-guru\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/bookmarks/tracking-database-changes-in-flask-sqlalchemy-for-audit-logs/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/bookmarks/tracking-database-changes-in-flask-sqlalchemy-for-audit-logs/\"\u003etracking-database-changes-in-flask-sqlalchemy-for-audit-logs\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e%% End Waypoint %%\u003c/p\u003e\n"},{"title":"Arts","date_published":"2023-07-14T10:56:15+10:00","date_modified":"2023-08-10T17:50:23+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/art/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/art/","content_html":""},{"title":"Books","date_published":"2023-06-29T23:00:43+10:00","date_modified":"2023-08-06T16:41:16+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/books/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/books/","content_html":""},{"title":"Posts","date_published":"2023-06-11T00:00:00+10:00","date_modified":"2023-08-11T18:38:22+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/posts/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/posts/","content_html":""},{"title":"the art studio","date_published":"2023-05-31T00:00:00+10:00","date_modified":"2023-08-06T16:00:14+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/the-art-studio/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/the-art-studio/","content_html":"\u003cp\u003eIf you\u0026rsquo;ve been enjoying my work and finding it entertaining. Your support means the world to me, and I can\u0026rsquo;t thank you enough for being a part of this journey.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you want to stay connected and show your support, you can follow or supported me on \u003ca href=\"https://ko-fi.com/errbufferoverfl\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eKo-Fi\u003c/a\u003e. It\u0026rsquo;s a fantastic way to help me create more amazing content and keep the creative juices flowing.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"projects\"\u003eProjects\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"anarchic-illustrationsartanarchic-illustrationsmd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/art/anarchic-illustrations/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/art/anarchic-illustrations/\"\u003eAnarchic Illustrations\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eDrawings, prints and stickers promoting the abolition of traditional forms of government and institutions.\nAll my anarchic themed illustrations are available as high-res downloads, available under CC by 4.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"100-days-of-gouacheartone-hundered-days-of-gouachemd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/art/one-hundered-days-of-gouache/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/art/one-hundered-days-of-gouache/\"\u003e100 days of gouache\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eThe concept of a 100 days project is you commit to doing something consistently for 100 days straight. For a non sequential 100 days I created a [[notes/gouache|gouache]] painting using 100 Days of Drawing by Jennifer Lewis.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"character-studiesartcharacter-studiesmd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/art/character-studies/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/art/character-studies/\"\u003echaracter studies\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eLittle illustrations and spreads that have been created to explore the traits of characters, featuring my favourites from television shows, movies and my imagination.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"vegetable-portraitsartvegetable-portraitsmd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/art/vegetable-portraits/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/art/vegetable-portraits/\"\u003evegetable portraits\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003ePortraits of my favourite and seasonal vegetables created using a variety of artistic mediums, they act as consistent theme that records changes in art style.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"work-in-progressartwork-in-progressmd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/art/work-in-progress/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/art/work-in-progress/\"\u003ework in progress\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eWork that is still in progress and being worked on.\nFreedom is not Given its TakenCheck it out on Ko-Fi → \u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"mediums\"\u003eMediums\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"gouachenotesgouachemd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/notes/gouache/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/notes/gouache/\"\u003egouache\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eGouache is a water based medium made of pigment, water and a binding agent, normally gum arabic or dextrin.\nGouache is similar to watercolour in that it can be re-hydrated and it infuses with the paper.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"woodblocknoteswoodblockmd\"\u003e\u003ca\n  href=\"/notes/woodblock/\"\n  rel=\"noopener\" class=\"internal-link\"\n  data-src=\"/notes/woodblock/\"\u003ewoodblock\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"desc\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eA technique originally developed in China as a way of printing on textiles and later on paper, the oldest surviving fragments to survive date back to the Han dynasty (before 220).\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n"},{"title":"the antilibrary","date_published":"2023-05-28T00:00:00+10:00","date_modified":"2023-08-06T16:00:03+10:00","id":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/the-antilibrary/","url":"https://garden.errbufferoverfl.me/the-antilibrary/","content_html":"\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ea scholar conscious of the power of [their] antilibrary is not concerned with treating knowledge as a property to possess or consume; rather [\u0026hellip;] how much you don’t know—and how to find out that information when you need it.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e- Giovanni da Col, HAU: Journal of Ethnographic Theory\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"before-you-begin\"\u003eBefore you begin…\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe notes and summaries included in these pages are snippets that remind me, or help me relate and explore high-level concepts. They aren\u0026rsquo;t a summary of the chapter or book! If you look through these notes and like the ideas, disagree with them, or you find yourself synthesising new ideas, I recommend you read the whole book!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"up-next\"\u003eUp Next\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"current\"\u003eCurrent\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"section-ul\"\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/ghost-work.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/books/ghost-work/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/books/ghost-work/\"\u003eGhost Work\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003e\u0026ldquo;A startling exposé of the invisible human workforce that powers the web\u0026ndash;and how to bring it out of the shadows. Hidden beneath the surface of the internet, a new, stark reality is looming\u0026ndash;one that cuts to the very heart of our endless debates about the impact of AI.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/book/\"\u003eBook\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/technology/\"\u003eTechnology\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/non-fiction/\"\u003eNon-Fiction\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/economics/\"\u003eEconomics\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/business/\"\u003eBusiness\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/labor/\"\u003eLabor\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/anthropology/\"\u003eAnthropology\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/politics/\"\u003ePolitics\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/sociology/\"\u003eSociology\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/artificial-intelligence/\"\u003eArtificial Intelligence\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"past\"\u003ePast\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"section-ul\"\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/the-feminist-and-the-sex-offender.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/books/the-feminist-and-the-sex-offender/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/books/the-feminist-and-the-sex-offender/\"\u003eThe Feminist and the Sex Offender\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eIn the era of Me Too and mass incarceration, The Feminist and the Sex Offender makes a powerful feminist case for accountability without punishment and sexual safety and pleasure without injustice.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/book/\"\u003eBook\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/non-fiction/\"\u003eNon-Fiction\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/feminisim/\"\u003eFeminisim\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/politics/\"\u003ePolitics\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/philosophy/\"\u003ePhilosophy\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/theory/\"\u003eTheory\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/feminist-theory/\"\u003eFeminist Theory\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/gender/\"\u003eGender\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/social-justice/\"\u003eSocial Justice\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/academia/\"\u003eAcademia\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/anarchic-agreements-a-field-guide-to-collective-organising.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/books/anarchic-agreements-a-field-guide-to-collective-organising/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/books/anarchic-agreements-a-field-guide-to-collective-organising/\"\u003eAnarchic Agreements, a Field Guide to Collective Organising\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eA new world is possible and not just in our hearts. Anarchic Agreements is a quintessential field guide for the revolution, answering the practical questions often left out of works of political theory and philosophy.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/book/\"\u003eBook\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/non-fiction/\"\u003eNon-Fiction\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/political-science/\"\u003ePolitical Science\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/anarchy/\"\u003eAnarchy\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/anarchism/\"\u003eAnarchism\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/constitutions/\"\u003eConstitutions\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/history-and-theory/\"\u003eHistory and Theory\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/lost-in-work-escaping-capitalism.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/books/lost-in-work-escaping-capitalism/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/books/lost-in-work-escaping-capitalism/\"\u003eLost in Work Escaping Capitalism\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003e\u0026lsquo;Work hard, get paid.\u0026rsquo; It\u0026rsquo;s simple. Self-evident. But it\u0026rsquo;s also a lie—at least for most of us. For young people today, the old assumptions are crumbling; hard work in school no longer guarantees a secure, well-paying job in the future.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/book/\"\u003eBook\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/non-fiction/\"\u003eNon-Fiction\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/politics/\"\u003ePolitics\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/sociology/\"\u003eSociology\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/economics/\"\u003eEconomics\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/history/\"\u003eHistory\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/philosophy/\"\u003ePhilosophy\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/feminism/\"\u003eFeminism\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/labor/\"\u003eLabor\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/theory/\"\u003eTheory\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/activism/\"\u003eActivism\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/revolution-at-point-zero.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/books/revolution-at-point-zero/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/books/revolution-at-point-zero/\"\u003eRevolution at Point Zero\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eWritten between 1974 and 2016, Revolution at Point Zero collects four decades of research and theorising on the nature of housework, social reproduction, and women’s struggles on this terrain—to escape it, to better its conditions, to reconstruct it in ways that provide an alternative to capitalist relations.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/book/\"\u003eBook\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/non-fiction/\"\u003eNon-Fiction\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/social-science/\"\u003eSocial Science\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/feminism/\"\u003eFeminism\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/nonfiction/\"\u003eNonfiction\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/politics/\"\u003ePolitics\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/philosophy/\"\u003ePhilosophy\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/theory/\"\u003eTheory\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/essays/\"\u003eEssays\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/gender/\"\u003eGender\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"incomplete\"\u003eIncomplete\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"section-ul\"\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/expect-resistance-a-crimethinc-field-manual.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/books/expect-resistance-a-crimethinc-field-manual/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/books/expect-resistance-a-crimethinc-field-manual/\"\u003eExpect Resistance: A Crimethink Field Manual\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eExpect Resistance is not one but three books, each of which may be read as a complete work unto itself. The first book, printed in standard black ink, continues the inquiry into modern life and its discontents begun in Days of War, Nights of Love.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"tags\"\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/book/\"\u003eBook\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/political-science/\"\u003ePolitical Science\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/politics/\"\u003ePolitics\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/non-fiction/\"\u003eNon-Fiction\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/anarchism/\"\u003eAnarchism\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/philosophy/\"\u003ePhilosophy\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/activism/\"\u003eActivism\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/social-justice/\"\u003eSocial Justice\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/feminism/\"\u003eFeminism\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"/tags/counter-culture/\"\u003eCounter Culture\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli class=\"section-li\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"section\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-img\"\u003e\n                    \u003cimg src=\"/imgs/the-age-of-surveillance-capitalism.png\" alt=\"This image is missing alt text.\" width=\"200vw\"\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class=\"desc\" style=\"padding-left: 2em;\"\u003e\n                \u003ch3\u003e\u003ca href=\"/books/the-age-of-surveillance-capitalism/\" class=\"internal-link\" data-src=\"/books/the-age-of-surveillance-capitalism/\"\u003eThe Age of Surveillance Capitalism\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n                \u003cp style=\"padding-bottom: 1em; padding-top: 1em;\"\u003eThe challenges to humanity posed by the digital future, the first detailed examination of the unprecedented form of power called \u0026lsquo;surveillance capitalism,\u0026rsquo; and the quest by powerful corporations to predict and control us.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n     